# --- OcbGS additions ---
# The server recompiles the CUDA extensions fresh via setup.sh, so all build
# artifacts (compiled objects, egg-info, build/dist dirs) stay out of git.
# `*.so` and `*__pycache__*` above already cover the binaries; these add the rest.
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
*.egg-link
dist/
build/
.pytest_cache/
.python-version

# Real-time SIBR viewer: ~16 MB of vendored C++ source, not needed for headless
# training or the test suite. Delete this line (and run
# `git add -f ocbgs/SIBR_viewers`) if you ever want to version the viewer.
SIBR_viewers/